{"tid":2259893,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖應否同另一半報備／交帶？","createTime":"2020-10-27T07:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T17:56:13.000Z","uid":85934,"like":225,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"243d9b420d11d6f5e9f297448cddf80b4847edb6","tid":2259893,"uid":85934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"最近見到人討論，有啲人覺得同另一半報到／交帶好似多咗個阿媽咁，尤其話男仔唔中意畀人問去邊，好似畀人check 住，同埋好chur<br />\n<br />\n但另一方面覺得有交帶係好正常，都係比對方安全感嘅表現，唔係要知你幾時返，chur 你幾時返屋企，連對方去咗邊都唔知，唔會好冇安全感咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有交帶係應該<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚chur，唔鍾意比人控制"},{"pid":"470194800034be8885b838daf599b10d386094ec","tid":2259893,"uid":21187,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:22:51.000Z","msg":"唔交帶無所謂<br />\n咁咪搵個接受到唔交帶嘅另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956b6e45af3f2f596e2209627c2f857b5a6d6781","tid":2259893,"uid":103613,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:24:18.000Z","msg":"人夾人啫<br />\n對方無所謂既咪ok囉"},{"pid":"2180d844a57324dcc91cce862c17cf00342a922b","tid":2259893,"uid":75597,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"我老公返工係用唔到電話果種<br />\n拍拖果時已經冇報備<br />\n最多一齊出完街返屋企果時話佢聽返到未<br />\n人夾人姐<br />\n試過個ex，我一路同佢講電話<br />\n返到入屋放低電話叉電，去沖涼<br />\n十幾分鐘出返黎佢不停msg我話唔知我去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3b9f7c52059f8110231b018d6ef20045838c14","tid":2259893,"uid":149357,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"大家自動自覺報備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n約左咩人 有咩活動 <br />\n增加透明度 <br />\n大家都有安全感唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鐘意自然想咩都同對方講架啦"},{"pid":"b945eb42a0c83f20db14c72f6739212b89ffaaba","tid":2259893,"uid":50154,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score